                    <p class="mb-6 text-lg leading-8">
                        Vui lòng liên hệ với chúng tôi qua các kênh sau đây nếu bạn gặp vấn đề liên quan đến chất lượng sản phẩm
                        hoặc chất lượng phục vụ. Cảm ơn bạn đã chọn Nét cafe.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-10 text-lg">
                        <span class="block mb-2">Tel: <a href="" class="hover:text-yellow-600 transition">012-213-0989</a></span>
                        <span class="block">Email: <a href="" class="hover:text-yellow-600 transition">netcafe@company.com</a></span>
                    </p>
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <a href="https://www.google.com/maps" class="inline-block text-white text-2xl pl-10 pr-12 py-6 rounded-lg transition tm-bg-green">
                            <i class="fas fa-map-marked-alt mr-8"></i>
                            Open Maps
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1 rounded-xl p-12 pb-14 m-5 bg-black bg-opacity-50 tm-item-container">
                    <form action="" method="POST" class="text-lg">
                        <input type="text" name="name" class="input w-full bg-black border-b bg-opacity-0 text-white px-0 py-4 mb-4 tm-border-gold" placeholder="Tên" required="" />
                        <input type="email" name="email" class="input w-full bg-black border-b bg-opacity-0 text-white px-0 py-4 mb-4 tm-border-gold" placeholder="Email" required="" />
                        <textarea rows="6" name="message" class="input w-full bg-black border-b bg-opacity-0 text-white px-0 py-4 mb-4 tm-border-gold" placeholder="Nội dung..." required=""></textarea>
                        <div class="text-right">
                            <button type="submit" class="text-white hover:text-yellow-500 transition">Gửi</button>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

